profile:
Hummel’s Moving is a full-service moving and storage company. Our company has been in business for over 25 years, since January 1989.



We offer fully licensed and insured moving services for your home, apartment and office, including:

Moving
Packing
Heated storage
Packing supplies
Piano/organ moving
Assembly & disassembly


Great Canadian Van Lines Agent

Moving cross-country? Hummel’s Moving is proud to serve as an agent for Great Canadian Van Lines, Canada’s leading moving company. When you’re undergoing a long distance move, turn your move over to our trusted experts.



Whether your move is local, cross-province or cross-country, our more than 26 years of experience means we’re equipped to handle all aspects of the move professionally and efficiently. Please contact us today to discuss your move.
